casebody.data:
In the Matter of Howard W. Chan (Admitted as Howard W. H. Chan), a Suspended Attorney.

[— NYS2d —]

—Application for reinstatement granted, and petitioner reinstated as an attorney and counselor-at-law in the State of New York, effective immediately. No opinion. Concur — Sullivan, J. P., Mazzarelli, Wallach, Andrias and Buckley, JJ.
